{"tid":2367421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"73艘澳洲煤船為卸貨等足半年 下場卻很悽涼","createTime":"2021-01-15T10:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T22:48:29.000Z","uid":225931,"like":120,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"4feed8055f5f51ed541a331129080f7bfcada271","tid":2367421,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:33:20.000Z","msg":"中澳關係緊張下，中國全面叫停進口澳洲煤碳，大批未能趕及清關的煤船，被迫在中國的沿海滯留。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲媒體報道，北京當局已向73艘船、近800萬噸澳洲煤炭的貨主明確表示，他們的貨物將不會在中國卸貨，意味著這批煤炭要以更低價尋找新的買家，否則只會血本無歸。報道指，北京的決定加劇了近1,500名水手的人道主義危機，他們大部分人自去年6月起已被困在海上，且一直被禁止上岸。"},{"pid":"4d5dae2ae97511a276813427e2fb4e64ebb72b0b","tid":2367421,"uid":225931,"like":147,"dislike":3,"score":144,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"一早轉泊其他國家 <br />\n再經第三方轉賣俾中國咪無事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab33ba7a9b6ab55db42dab4379a8691f3e730e3e","tid":2367421,"uid":6063,"like":156,"dislike":4,"score":152,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"問題係，呢批貨班中國韭菜一早已經比哂錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家轉賣澳洲係一批貨賺兩次錢"},{"pid":"22d8c8f2772a2be678b91ac18a03edfdc6651aea","tid":2367421,"uid":387826,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"唔好要咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837207b13550f4bf90a8a07126a35796cb049606","tid":2367421,"uid":25601,"like":3,"dislike":51,"score":-48,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"放左咁耐仲用唔用到呀"},{"pid":"2047d5a0badfde8317aa7e1ba945f76683cc7211","tid":2367421,"uid":36058,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"837207b13550f4bf90a8a07126a35796cb049606","tid":2367421,"uid":25601,"like":3,"dislike":51,"score":-48,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"放左咁耐仲用唔用到呀"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"煤唔會過期"},{"pid":"6362e2b53546f705d3c8c37310ee530bdb129d65","tid":2367421,"uid":33916,"like":13,"dis